{"tid":783902,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣早出嚟做嘢好易無咗原本嘅朋友","createTime":"2018-08-18T02:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T07:41:07.000Z","uid":15425,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae72b8657d99545f7685dc4f688bbce4ceeb12cb","tid":783902,"uid":15425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"我踏入社會嘅時候佢哋仲讀書<br />\n嗰時陣中會覺得好唔適應同吃力<br />\n但係我同佢哋分享佢哋根本唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到而家我事業開始有起色<br />\n 佢地就經歷緊我以前捱嗰個時候<br />\n根本無可能分享到嗰種喜悅<br />\n加上大家嘅理念開始唔同<br />\n所以覺得同呢班朋友好似越行越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72de1e876f1d39e6a51066412d353979f401146","tid":783902,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7642a80750f002938890cc18c8bfc58e890fa18","tid":783902,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03e968ae66a58bc5a7d356bed31b3d3afe9c612b","tid":783902,"uid":15425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"每次出去嘅時候都係傾以前 <br />\n但覺得經營左咁耐既關係無左又好可惜"}]}